{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a8/46/87086_crt_2d9Ud.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/a8/46/87086_crt_2d9Ud.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a8/46/87086_crt_2d9Ud.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a8/46/87086_crt_2d9Ud.jpg"},"name":"ガレット・レヴォ","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/06/29/4015_prsn_4TZox.jpg?r=1638448222","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/06/29/4015_prsn_4TZox.jpg?r=1638448222","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/06/29/4015_prsn_4TZox.jpg?r=1638448222","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/06/29/4015_prsn_4TZox.jpg?r=1638448222"},"name":"櫻井孝宏","short_summary":"爱知县冈崎市老家的本业是米店，店名为“樱井米谷店”，在当地小有名气。\r\n初中时的一个冬天，怕冷的他擅自把酒精灯里的液体倒在理科实验室的桌子上，点起火取暖，引响了火灾报警器，被赶来的老师狠狠教训了一顿。于是在老师的国语课上捣乱报复，夸张地朗读课文，实在听不过去的老师求他：“拜托，别念得跟声优似的好不好！”——这话对那时的樱井冲击很大，给他留下了声优不过是连小孩子都做得来的简单工作的印象。所以高中毕业后，乐得找轻松的樱井选择进入东京的声优专科学校。待迈入这一行，他才吐血地发现，且不说成为佼佼者，就是普通从业者也得掌握高超的专业技巧。\r\n2005年8月《最终幻想VII：降临之子》于第62届威尼斯影展参展。樱井以担任主角配音的身份，成为继山寺宏一后第2位踏上星光大道的日本籍声优。\r\n虽然戴着眼镜，可是樱井二眼视力皆为2.0，植田佳奈笑称那是“骗人眼镜”。那付眼镜的意义是“梦想与希望与对声迷们的爱”。\r\n最初的错误是BL DRAMA制作社Inter communications（inter桑）的一张drama的BK上打成了樱井考宏，之后《无法逃离的背叛》某个活动的官方网站上亦把樱井孝宏的名字写成“樱井考宏”，所以有昵称考哥，而并非是他的名字中的“孝”字与“考”字很像才有此外号。\r\n桜井(sakurai)，桜井さん（sakurai san），sakura i san，樱13","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":4015,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87086},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c5/6e/87087_crt_l5RR1.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/c5/6e/87087_crt_l5RR1.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c5/6e/87087_crt_l5RR1.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c5/6e/87087_crt_l5RR1.jpg"},"name":"ヴァルト・パークス","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/bf/00/3818_prsn_vlWlO.jpg?r=1669378022","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/bf/00/3818_prsn_vlWlO.jpg?r=1669378022","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bf/00/3818_prsn_vlWlO.jpg?r=1669378022","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/bf/00/3818_prsn_vlWlO.jpg?r=1669378022"},"name":"福山潤","short_summary":"福山润（1978年11月26日－）是一名日本男性声优。大阪府高槻市出身。2000年于21岁时加入PRODUCTION baobab，2011年退出和PRODUCTION baobab，并与森川智之共同设立AXL ONE事务所。2018年3月31日，与立花慎之介一起离开AXL ONE；同年4月1日，与立花合伙成立小型事务所“BLACK SHIP”。\r\n初试啼声的动画作品是1998年的《罗德斯岛战记》。初次担任主角的动画作品是2000年到2001年的《无敌王TRI-ZENON》，饰演神威章。此部作品同时也是无职身分的福山润再次以声优身分回归声优界的复归代表作。而令福山润真正登上事业上第一次颠峰的角色，则是《反叛的鲁路修》中的腹黑王子鲁路修，他就是凭着这个角色而获得了第一回声优悬赏奖的最佳男声优。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":3818,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87087},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/ec/68/87088_crt_JWlVH.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/ec/68/87088_crt_JWlVH.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/ec/68/87088_crt_JWlVH.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/ec/68/87088_crt_JWlVH.jpg"},"name":"ヴィザルガ","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":87088},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/d0/ce/87089_crt_w1v2P.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/d0/ce/87089_crt_w1v2P.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d0/ce/87089_crt_w1v2P.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/d0/ce/87089_crt_w1v2P.jpg"},"name":"ライム","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b3/1a/5745_prsn_0GjVg.jpg?r=1643856929","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/b3/1a/5745_prsn_0GjVg.jpg?r=1643856929","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b3/1a/5745_prsn_0GjVg.jpg?r=1643856929","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b3/1a/5745_prsn_0GjVg.jpg?r=1643856929"},"name":"佐倉綾音","short_summary":"佐仓绫音（さくら あやね）是日本的女性声优，1994年1月29日出生及成长于东京都；曾为[url=www.imenterprise.jp]I'm Enterprise[/url]旗下声优，2022年2月1日移籍至[url=www.aoni.co.jp]青二Production[/url]。\r\n\r\n[b]经历[/b]\r\n中学时所属剧团东俳，[url=https://nichinare.com/]日本播音演技研究所[/url]出身。《Dottoai广播》第45代主持人。2011年，在TV动画《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/8990]食梦者玛利[/url]》出演[url=https://bgm.tv/character/10571]玛利·梦魔[/url]，首次出演主角。同年在剧场版动画《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/12544]萤火之森[/url]》中出演[url=https://bgm.tv/character/15896]竹川萤[/url]，首次担当主役。\r\n其他代表作品有《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/88287]请问您今天要来点兔子吗？[/url]》[url=https://bgm.tv/character/23647]保登心爱[/url]、《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/78405]悠哉日常大王[/url]》[url=https://bgm.tv/character/21370]越谷夏海[/url]、《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/37685]心理测量者[/url]》[url=https://bgm.tv/character/18476]霜月美佳[/url]、《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/54433]我的青春恋爱物语果然有问题[/url]》[url=https://bgm.tv/character/26090]一色彩羽[/url]、《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/120925]夏洛特[/url]》[url=https://bgm.tv/character/29511]友利奈绪[/url]、《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/100444]四月是你的谎言[/url]》[url=https://bgm.tv/character/26004]泽部椿[/url]等。\r\n\r\n[b]其他[/b]\r\n昵称“あやねる（ayaneru）”是由[url=https://bgm.tv/person/4950]冈本信彦[/url]（《[url=https://bgm.tv/subject/8990]食梦者玛利[/url]》的合演者）给予的。关于昵称（本人说）“没什么特别的”。“あやねる”只是“绫音”和“睡觉（寝る）”的组合。\r\n完全的百合脑、百合控，非常喜欢[url=https://bgm.tv/person/4765]花泽香菜[/url]。\r\n爱好读书，特技是插图。","career":["seiyu"],"id":5745,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87089},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/fd/9f/87090_crt_4o0v6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/fd/9f/87090_crt_4o0v6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/fd/9f/87090_crt_4o0v6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/fd/9f/87090_crt_4o0v6.jpg"},"name":"クック","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/1a/1f/8433_prsn_F4W4E.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/1a/1f/8433_prsn_F4W4E.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1a/1f/8433_prsn_F4W4E.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/1a/1f/8433_prsn_F4W4E.jpg"},"name":"小平有希","short_summary":"","career":["seiyu"],"id":8433,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87090},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/fb/37/87091_crt_1L2Mi.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/fb/37/87091_crt_1L2Mi.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/fb/37/87091_crt_1L2Mi.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/fb/37/87091_crt_1L2Mi.jpg"},"name":"アバレス・レヴォ","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/88/5b/5168_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/88/5b/5168_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/88/5b/5168_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/88/5b/5168_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"喜山茂雄","short_summary":"","career":["seiyu"],"id":5168,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87091},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e8/da/87092_crt_t8OzQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/e8/da/87092_crt_t8OzQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/e8/da/87092_crt_t8OzQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/e8/da/87092_crt_t8OzQ.jpg"},"name":"ルシアン・パークス","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/d7/61/22598_prsn_ngN1w.jpg?r=1681413070","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/d7/61/22598_prsn_ngN1w.jpg?r=1681413070","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d7/61/22598_prsn_ngN1w.jpg?r=1681413070","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/d7/61/22598_prsn_ngN1w.jpg?r=1681413070"},"name":"増元拓也","short_summary":"賢プロダクション　所属\r\n\r\n出身地：広島県\r\n特技・趣味：殺陣、スノーボード","career":["seiyu"],"id":22598,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87092},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/09/1f/87093_crt_Ga7FF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/09/1f/87093_crt_Ga7FF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/09/1f/87093_crt_Ga7FF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/09/1f/87093_crt_Ga7FF.jpg"},"name":"アルス・グリンホルン","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/d8/42/4495_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/d8/42/4495_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d8/42/4495_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/d8/42/4495_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"緒乃冬華","short_summary":"緒乃 冬華（おの ふゆか、1978年1月13日 - ）は、日本の女性声優。アクロス エンタテインメント所属。北海道札幌市出身。既婚。旧名は大浦 冬華（おおうら ふゆか）\r\n\r\n2009年4月まで東京俳優生活協同組合に所属していた。同年6月よりアクロス エンタテインメント所属。また、俳協所属以前は劇団アルターエゴにも所属していた。\r\n2011年7月25日付のブログで結婚したことを発表した。2013年8月6日に女児を出産。\r\n川澄綾子とは猫好き仲間であり、一緒に食事したり旅行もする。\r\n看護師・保健師資格を持つ。また、心屋仁之助に傾倒しており、心屋塾の心屋リセットカウンセリングマスターの資格も持ち、ブログでその内容に言及することも多い。\r\n2016年3月より、旧姓（本名）だった「大浦冬華」から「緒乃冬華」へと改名した。","career":["seiyu"],"id":4495,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87093},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/73/4e/87094_crt_la32z.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/73/4e/87094_crt_la32z.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/73/4e/87094_crt_la32z.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/73/4e/87094_crt_la32z.jpg"},"name":"モルガン・バクスター","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9e/e9/5434_prsn_Q1KON.jpg?r=1422087468","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/9e/e9/5434_prsn_Q1KON.jpg?r=1422087468","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/e9/5434_prsn_Q1KON.jpg?r=1422087468","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9e/e9/5434_prsn_Q1KON.jpg?r=1422087468"},"name":"阪口周平","short_summary":"","career":["seiyu"],"id":5434,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87094},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/ae/42/87095_crt_mX6Mx.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/ae/42/87095_crt_mX6Mx.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/ae/42/87095_crt_mX6Mx.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/ae/42/87095_crt_mX6Mx.jpg"},"name":"スノウ・マクレイン","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/5b/8c/14918_prsn_1V1dU.jpg?r=1676109778","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/5b/8c/14918_prsn_1V1dU.jpg?r=1676109778","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/5b/8c/14918_prsn_1V1dU.jpg?r=1676109778","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/5b/8c/14918_prsn_1V1dU.jpg?r=1676109778"},"name":"長縄まりあ","short_summary":"日本的女性声优，爱知县出身。I'm Enterprise所属。\r\n\r\n成为声优的契机是在国中时代参与呼吁禁烟运动的时候，曾被路上的人称赞 “你的声音很棒”，同时在学校也常被同学模仿，因此知道自己的声音并不普通。\r\n就读日本播音演技研究所的基本科时，在进级审查中的试镜中合格，并加入I'm Enterprise。\r\n\r\n憧憬的声优为大谷育江与钉宫理惠。\r\n喜欢的食物是煎饼、零食。有在寿司店打工的经验。\r\n特别喜欢少年系的动画。\r\n2016年的访谈中提到今后想以演出吉祥物角色为目标。\r\n\r\n与同期出身的声优小泽亚李交情很好。同时与在《三坪房间的侵略者！？》演出的大森日雅、铃木绘理、田泽茉纯亦有深交。","career":["seiyu"],"id":14918,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87095},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/98/4f/87096_crt_qJkVs.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/98/4f/87096_crt_qJkVs.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/98/4f/87096_crt_qJkVs.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/98/4f/87096_crt_qJkVs.jpg"},"name":"グレアム・レオニード","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b4/3f/4607_prsn_4e4eB.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/b4/3f/4607_prsn_4e4eB.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b4/3f/4607_prsn_4e4eB.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b4/3f/4607_prsn_4e4eB.jpg"},"name":"白熊寛嗣","short_summary":"白熊 寛嗣（しろくま ひろし、1979年8月4日 - ）は、日本の男性声優。ぷろだくしょんバオバブ所属。神奈川県横浜市出身。血液型AB型。身長175cm。体重63kg。\r\n低く太めな声質が特徴で、父親役や中年男性など自身の年齢よりも高い人物を演じることが多い。\r\n\r\n2006年の『007』シリーズのソフト新録版では、当時20代でありながら50-70代の「Q」（デスモンド・リュウェリン）役というかなりの老け役を演じた。\r\n\r\n「白熊」は本名である。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":4607,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":87096},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/62/4f/87097_crt_BiUa4.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/62/4f/87097_crt_BiUa4.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/62/4f/87097_crt_BiUa4.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/62/4f/87097_crt_BiUa4.jpg"},"name":"ザイファー・トライ","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/82/32/36531_prsn_3xh0n.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/82/32/36531_prsn_3xh0n.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/82/32/36531_prsn_3xh0n.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/82/32/36531_prsn_